"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1932135-Olympics-2024-Amber-Rutter-Team-GB-skeet-BBC\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Team GBskeet shooter Amber Rutter questioned the absence of a VAR system in the2024 Olympicsfinal after controversially missing out on a gold medal on Sunday.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 160, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 64, \"end\": 67, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.8954002272459215e-15, \"text\": \"VAR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rutter won silver in Paris but was cruelly denied the Olympic title after slow-motion replays appeared to show she hit a shot that went down as the crucial miss in a final shoot-off.\", \"from\": 162, \"to\": 344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 183, \"end\": 188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999836291, \"rank\": 1.620653395557931e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 26-year-old finished the final tied on 55 shots from 60 targets with Chile's Francisca Crovetto Chadid, sparking the dramatic shoot-off.\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 486, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 419, \"end\": 424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"score\": 0.7764293970538287, \"rank\": 0.24837057206564636, \"text\": \"Chile\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\"}, {\"begin\": 427, \"end\": 445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francisca_Crovetto\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Francisca Crovetto\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francisca_Crovetto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francisca_Crovetto\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Three rounds passed, and the pair remained tied until Rutter was called to have missed a shot, which she was convinced she had hit.\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 619, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pick up your ultimate guide to the Olympics!\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 665, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Going for Gold provides the day-by-day rundown of what's on and when.\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 735, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clickhereto buy.\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 752, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Replays seemingly showed that the Brit was correct to contest the call, but the judges did not overturn their decision, leaving her disappointed.\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 899, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Crovetto Chadid then swept in, hitting both of her next shots to confirm Chile's first-ever shooting gold medal in controversial circumstances.\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 1044, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 974, \"end\": 979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"score\": 0.7764293970538287, \"rank\": 0.24837057206564636, \"text\": \"Chile\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The result left many viewers fuming andinsisting the Team GB star had been robbed, while the revelation that no VAR or Hawkeye system was in use at the Olympics also baffled those watching at home.\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1243, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1099, \"end\": 1106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999987949088776, \"rank\": 1.129764202156648e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1158, \"end\": 1161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.8954002272459215e-15, \"text\": \"VAR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\"}, {\"begin\": 1165, \"end\": 1172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Natty_Bumppo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.9357351919519855e-18, \"text\": \"Hawkeye\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Natty_Bumppo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Natty_Bumppo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rutter - the first woman to win a shooting medal for Team GB - appeared on BBC1 on Monday morning, insisting she was proud of her achievement as frustrating as the outcome was.\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1421, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1320, \"end\": 1324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\", \"score\": 0.9998256458399509, \"rank\": 0.0001743845647420573, \"text\": \"BBC1\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So I managed to get into a shoot-off for the gold medal match.\", \"from\": 1423, \"to\": 1486, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We tied after our 60 targets and then we went into a shoot-off,\\\" Rutter explained.\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1569, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1615, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1616, \"to\": 1686, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1680, \"end\": 1685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999836291, \"rank\": 1.620653395557931e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1791, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1761, \"end\": 1773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9999559468991984, \"rank\": 4.405493470577409e-05, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1846, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We shoot a pair, and then we switch over.\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 1890, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was shooting against Fran from Chile, and I believe that I hit my last target.\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 1971, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1924, \"end\": 1929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"score\": 0.7764293970538287, \"rank\": 0.24837057206564636, \"text\": \"Chile\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chile\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Unfortunately the ref did not see it.\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 2011, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I turned round and tried to appeal it but the ref did not see it and they called it as a loss.\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2106, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"From the reaction I have had today from people saying they did also see that target break, it is painful but this is what happens in sport.\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2248, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just part of the game.\\\"\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2277, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rutter - who was in the studio with Tommy, her first child who incredibly arrived just three months before she competed in Paris - also mentioned that she wasn't the only skeet shooter who felt aggrieved.\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2483, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2402, \"end\": 2407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999836291, \"rank\": 1.620653395557931e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She added: \\\"I know it wasn't just myself affected.\", \"from\": 2485, \"to\": 2535, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There were other athletes in the final where they believe they hit shots as well and they were not given.\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2641, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It shows how VAR systems are.\", \"from\": 2642, \"to\": 2671, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2655, \"end\": 2658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.8954002272459215e-15, \"text\": \"VAR\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Video_assistant_referee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's something we did have but I am not quite sure where it was this time?\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2748, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just do not want to take away all the hard work that has gone into this medal.\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2829, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's something to be celebrated, not stewed on.\\\"\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 2878, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 2989, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2990, \"to\": 3066, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 3067, \"to\": 3099, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  Rutter was surprised by her husband and Tommy after the final, and she confirmed that they were set to enjoy a day of sightseeing around Paris before heading back to the UK.\", \"from\": 31